data.description: Immaculately kept home in Woodland Heights is looking for a new owner. Coming in through the front door and into the foyer, to the right is a flex room, currently being used as an office. To the left is the separate dining room. This room connects to the breakfast area off the kitchen. The kitchen has tons of cabinets, topped with granite, a work island and a coffee bar! Down the hallway is a half bath and laundry room with mud sink and matching built in cabinets. Circling around behind the stairs you enter into the sunporch which has access around the fireplace back into the living room. The living room has built in book cases and leads back into the foyer, kitchen and hallway. Down the hallway takes you to the primary bedroom with 2 walk in closets and an ensuite bath with garden tub, double vanities and separate shower. Past the primary bedroom at the end of the hall is a full bath just outside the second bedroom. As you go upstairs, it opens up to the loft area with a bedroom and attached bath on each side. Out back is a tiled deck area overlooking the fully fenced back yard. Add to this the 2 car carport with attached storage and a brand new HVAC system on the main floor in October 2023 and this is the first and last one you will need to look at! Current loan is VA and it is assumable.
